{"tid":466061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普:願就南海主權爭議擔當仲裁角色","createTime":"2017-11-12T07:51:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T03:09:49.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb7fa835f98f381d2f3e486cd87ee8bf683e318","tid":466061,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"特朗普:願就南海主權爭議擔當仲裁角色<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1699945/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A%E9%A1%98%E5%B0%B1%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%93%94%E7%95%B6%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1699945%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%253A%25E9%25A1%2598%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%2593%2594%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25A3%2581%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%2589%25B2&d=9rRABI4mxnU312pk21FbRL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=5517d34e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1699945/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%3A%E9%A1%98%E5%B0%B1%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E4%B8%BB%E6%AC%8A%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E6%93%94%E7%95%B6%E4%BB%B2%E8%A3%81%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普轉抵河內對越南進行國事訪問，在與越南國家主席陳大光進行雙邊會談時表示，知悉中國與越南等東南亞多國，就南海主權出現爭議，願意協助各方在南海問題上擔當調停及仲裁角色。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普在Twitter帖文指出，他在出席亞太經合組織(APEC)領導人峰會時，中國國家主席習近平稱正加強對北韓的制裁，希望北韓最終可達至無核化。特朗普說，北韓領導人金正恩語帶侮辱斥他年紀老，但他從來沒說金正恩矮及肥，是因為他努力嘗試與金正恩交朋友，希望有朝一日可以實現。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，在APEC期間與俄羅斯總統普京會面，就敍利亞的情況有很好的交談，希望美國所有懷恨及愚昧的人明白，與俄羅斯保持良好關係，是好事而非壞事，因為俄羅斯在解決北韓、敍利亞、烏克蘭及反恐問題上，都可以提供很大幫助。"},{"pid":"894a470e6b9ce7c9f839878826dd2aaf6f0be18f","tid":466061,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c01836a1ed4eaca089766516e43aa969b68e5e","tid":466061,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://st2.depositphotos.com/2159851/7731/v/950/depositphotos_77315270-stock-illustration-corrupt-referee-taking-a-bribe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fst2.depositphotos.com%2F2159851%2F7731%2Fv%2F950%2Fdepositphotos_77315270-stock-illustration-corrupt-referee-taking-a-bribe.jpg&h=910d70e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07776f26a05c584856e08537ef7beafa93f599d3","tid":466061,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"仲你老母，收咗中國咁多錢仲唔成隻狗咁"},{"pid":"151ec20b51e44a1c67dfa2df19cb34c4284a5fa7","tid":466061,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T07:56:37.000Z","msg":"次次訪問完支那就反面"},{"pid":"0f4061fc9df2acac1181128718ec441b3112931d","tid":466061,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T08:01:52.000Z","msg":"好似講緊 南海 我大哂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f30808224845bdfbd3019813d74fdb02feabf4","tid":466061,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:55:14.000Z","msg":"好似小學風紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbd0151e51d7cc318d1a4aef27655ac3b8889ee","tid":466061,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似小學風紀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/105522_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F105522_394659692a460258b45a99f1424ea357.jpg&h=175be8ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e8b4cd0297122bdf0b87e